# ==============================================================================
# 1. Global Ignore: Block everything by default
# ==============================================================================
*

# ==============================================================================
# 2. Whitelist: Structural Repository Layout & Base Files
# ==============================================================================
!*/
!README.md
!LICENSE
!.gitignore
!Makefile
!*.md

# ==============================================================================
# 3. Whitelist: Source Code & Scripting Assets
# ==============================================================================
# SystemVerilog, Verilog, and Header files
!*.sv
!*.v
!*.vh

# C/C++ Software files
!*.cpp
!*.h
!*.c

# Automation & Tool constraints
!*.tcl
!*.xdc
!*.wcfg

# ==============================================================================
# 4. Explicit Tool-Generated Blacklist (Safety Net for directory overrides)
# ==============================================================================
.Xil/
*.log
*.jou
*.pb
*.dir/
*.str
*.vcd
*.wdb
xsim.dir/
xsim_*.backup.cdb
